{"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Manages PID files for tracking running virtual machines."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"topicSections":[{"title":"Type Properties","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/fileName"],"anchor":"Type-Properties"},{"title":"Type Methods","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isProcessAlive(_:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isRunning(bundleURL:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/read(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/remove(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/terminate(bundleURL:gracePeriod:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/write(to:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/writeAndEnsureCapacity(bundleURL:vmDirectory:)"],"anchor":"Type-Methods"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/pidfile"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"PIDFile","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PIDFile","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:15SpooktacularKit7PIDFileO","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PIDFile"}],"symbolKind":"enum"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PIDFile","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"over